race.comment: MAJOR ORSON (1) was out of the placings last time when eighth at Ballarat (26.04) but scored four back at this track (26.09). Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Has claims if he runs up to expectations. ASTON SURPASS (3) has missed the frame at his last couple but wasn't beaten far three back when second (25.90) at Warrnambool in a Grade 5. Can find the frame this time. JUNGLE FIREBALL (5) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (26.64) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record here winning three races. Cannot be taken lightly. AUSSIE FLAME (8) is a surprise last-start placegetter who should be thereabouts.
